# Code Owners
# This file defines who is responsible for code in specific parts of the repository
# For more information, see: https://docs.github.com/en/repositories/managing-your-repositorys-settings-and-features/customizing-your-repository/about-code-owners

# Global owners (fallback for any file not covered by specific rules)
* @your-username

# Documentation
*.md @your-username @docs-team
docs/ @your-username @docs-team

# Configuration files
.github/ @your-username @devops-team
.vscode/ @your-username @devops-team
*.yml @your-username @devops-team
*.yaml @your-username @devops-team
*.json @your-username @devops-team

# Build and CI/CD
CMakeLists.txt @your-username @build-team
build.* @your-username @build-team
.pre-commit-config.yaml @your-username @devops-team

# Source code
src/ @your-username @dev-team
include/ @your-username @dev-team
*.cpp @your-username @dev-team
*.hpp @your-username @dev-team
*.h @your-username @dev-team
*.c @your-username @dev-team

# Tests
tests/ @your-username @qa-team
test/ @your-username @qa-team
*test* @your-username @qa-team

# Scripts
scripts/ @your-username @devops-team
*.sh @your-username @devops-team
*.ps1 @your-username @devops-team
*.cmd @your-username @devops-team
